        <defName>Marak_StandardMechadendrite</defName>
        <label>standard general mechadendrite</label>
        <labelNoun>a standard general mechadendrite</labelNoun>
        <description>An installed standard general mechadendrite. A unique plasteel-steel blend and advanced circuitry grant it exceptional agility and utility.</description>
